","key":"sjones","accountId":"557058:f5dce1b0-db45-4dd6-a0e8-3cea5effb5ce","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Steve Jones","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"This story is the starting point for managing cassandra so later stories will update various aspects of the changes made. There are some initial packaging changes required so that we do not break rpm builds.\r\n\r\nFor eucalyptus-cloud the following files are added with the shown permissions / ownership:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n#\r\n# ll -l /usr/libexec/eucalyptus/euca-cassandra \r\n-rwxr-xr-x. 1 root root 5325 Mar  1 23:19 /usr/libexec/eucalyptus/euca-cassandra\r\n#\r\n#\r\n# ls -dl /usr/share/eucalyptus/cassandra/\r\ndrwxr-xr-x. 2 root root 25 Mar  1 23:19 /usr/share/eucalyptus/cassandra/\r\n#\r\n#\r\n# ls -l /usr/share/eucalyptus/cassandra/\r\ntotal 8\r\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root root 4182 Mar  1 23:19 logback.xml\r\n#\r\n# ls -dl /var/lib/eucalyptus/cassandra/\r\ndrwx------. 6 eucalyptus eucalyptus 67 Mar  1 23:23 /var/lib/eucalyptus/cassandra/\r\n#\r\n#\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nThe libexec script is called from eucalyptus-cloud to start/stop cassandra, /usr/share/eucalyptus/cassandra/ contains static configuration files for cassandra that are not expected to be modified by users. /var/lib/eucalyptus/cassandra/ is added for cassandra data and generated configuration files.\r\n\r\nLog files for cassandra will be under /var/log/eucalyptus:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n# ll /var/log/eucalyptus/*cassandra*\r\n-rw-r--r--. 1 eucalyptus eucalyptus       0 Mar  1 23:23 /var/log/eucalyptus/cassandra-debug.log\r\n-rw-r--r--. 1 eucalyptus eucalyptus  340367 Mar  2 11:34 /var/log/eucalyptus/cassandra-gc.log.0.current\r\n-rw-r--r--. 1 eucalyptus eucalyptus   20507 Mar  2 00:34 /var/log/eucalyptus/cassandra.log\r\n-rw-r--r--. 1 eucalyptus eucalyptus 1518646 Mar  2 11:34 /var/log/eucalyptus/cassandra-system.log\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nPid/lock files are currently in /var/run/eucalyptus/:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n# ll /var/run/eucalyptus/cassandra*\r\n-rw-r--r--. 1 root       root       0 Mar  2 00:34 /var/run/eucalyptus/cassandra.lock\r\n-rw-r--r--. 1 eucalyptus eucalyptus 4 Mar  2 00:34 /var/run/eucalyptus/cassandra.pid\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nbut this usage will likely change should we switch to using systemd.\r\n\r\nThe creation of the following was removed:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n/var/lib/eucalyptus/webapps/\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nas this directory is unused since the removal of the admin console / credential download.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=sjones","name":"sjones","key":"sjones","accountId":"557058:f5dce1b0-db45-4dd6-a0e8-3cea5effb5ce","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Steve Jones","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2017-03-02T13:49:05.069-0600","updated":"2017-03-02T13:49:05.069-0600"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/54402/comment/118607","id":"118607","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=sjones","name":"sjones","key":"sjones","accountId":"557058:f5dce1b0-db45-4dd6-a0e8-3cea5effb5ce","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Steve Jones","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"To enable use of cassandra on qa builds, add a cassandra component on each cloud component with a clc or ufs. Alternatively you can put cassandra only on the clc and also set the cloud property:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nservices.simplequeue.db_to_use=euca-cassandra\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nThe version of cassandra we use currently is:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n# rpm -qi cassandra22-2.2.8-1.noarch\r\nName        : cassandra22\r\nVersion     : 2.2.8\r\nRelease     : 1\r\nArchitecture: noarch\r\nInstall Date: Wed 01 Mar 2017 11:07:38 PM PST\r\nGroup       : Development/Libraries\r\nSize        : 33919667\r\nLicense     : Apache Software License\r\nSignature   : RSA/SHA256, Fri 30 Sep 2016 10:21:03 AM PDT, Key ID 0ff0d86010782bd9\r\nSource RPM  : cassandra22-2.2.8-1.src.rpm\r\nBuild Date  : Thu 29 Sep 2016 10:52:45 AM PDT\r\nBuild Host  : host-10-200-175-77\r\nRelocations : (not relocatable)\r\nURL         : http://cassandra.apache.org/\r\nSummary     : Cassandra is a highly scalable, eventually consistent, distributed, structured key-value store.\r\nDescription :\r\nCassandra brings together the distributed systems technologies from Dynamo\r\nand the data model from Google's BigTable. Like Dynamo, Cassandra is\r\neventually consistent. Like BigTable, Cassandra provides a ColumnFamily-based\r\ndata model richer than typical key/value systems.\r\n\r\nFor more information see http://cassandra.apache.org/\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nWhen cassandra is available the cassandra service should be enabled on the cloud controller:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n#\r\n# euserv-describe-services --filter service-type=cassandra\r\nSERVICE  cassandra  eucalyptus  10.111.5.166  enabled  \r\n# \r\n{code}\r\n\r\nWhen cassanda is not available (i.e. rpm not installed) the cassanda service will show \"notready\".\r\n\r\nYou can check the status of the eucalyptus managed cassandra using:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n# /usr/libexec/eucalyptus/euca-cassandra status\r\ncassandra (pid  8376) is running...\r\n# \r\n{code}\r\n\r\nCassandra logs are available under /var/log/eucalyptus.\r\n\r\nWe are not currently using secure connections for cassandra so you can connect on the registration ip using:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n#\r\n# cqlsh 10.111.5.166 8787\r\nConnected to Eucalyptus.4.4.0.cassandra.464d8982d628ba05fe29048f188963d0ddb9c5d704c43ea8e459aca8c5f7370b at 10.111.5.166:8787.\r\n[cqlsh 5.0.1 | Cassandra 2.2.8 | CQL spec 3.3.1 | Native protocol v4]\r\nUse HELP for help.\r\ncqlsh> exit\r\n#\r\n#\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nWhen cassandra is not available (rpm not present) sqs will use postgres for persistence.\r\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=sjones","name":"sjones","key":"sjones","accountId":"557058:f5dce1b0-db45-4dd6-a0e8-3cea5effb5ce","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Steve Jones","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2017-03-03T11:37:55.591-0600","updated":"2017-03-03T11:37:55.591-0600"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/54402/comment/119440","id":"119440","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=sjones","name":"sjones","key":"sjones","accountId":"557058:f5dce1b0-db45-4dd6-a0e8-3cea5effb5ce","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Steve Jones","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"Installation changes were temporarily reverted to allow this story to be merged without any packaging work.\r\n\r\nThe details of cassandra use will be captured here:\r\n\r\nhttps://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/wiki/display/STS/Cassandra+5.0\r\n\r\nthe details mentioned in this story will change as development progresses.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=sjones","name":"sjones","key":"sjones","accountId":"557058:f5dce1b0-db45-4dd6-a0e8-3cea5effb5ce","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.ne